INSERT INTO compensados
SELECT saknr, blart, bldat, budat, azbet, dmbtr, sgtxt, belnr, azwae, hwaer, buzei, gjahr, compensado, record_id, signo
FROM (
    SELECT
        A.*,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY A.dmbtr ORDER BY A.dmbtr, A.blart) AS row_num
    FROM
        pa_bancarias A
    JOIN pa_bancarias B ON
        (A.sgtxt LIKE '$textoTipoDoc_A_1$%' OR A.sgtxt LIKE '$textoTipoDoc_A_2$%')
        AND (B.sgtxt LIKE '$textoTipoDoc_B_1$%' OR B.sgtxt LIKE '$textoTipoDoc_B_2$%')
        AND ((A.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$' AND B.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$') OR (A.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$' AND B.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$'))
    WHERE
        A.record_id <> B.record_id
        AND A.signo <> B.signo
        AND ABS(A.dmbtr - B.dmbtr) <= 0
        AND A.compensado = false
        AND B.compensado = false
) AS CompensacionesA
WHERE row_num = 1
UNION

FROM (
    SELECT
        B.*,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY A.dmbtr ORDER BY A.dmbtr, A.blart) AS row_num
    FROM
        pa_bancarias B
    JOIN pa_bancarias A ON
       (A.sgtxt LIKE '$textoTipoDoc_A_1$%' OR A.sgtxt LIKE '$textoTipoDoc_A_2$%')
        AND (B.sgtxt LIKE '$textoTipoDoc_B_1$%' OR B.sgtxt LIKE '$textoTipoDoc_B_2$%')
        AND ((A.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$' AND B.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$') OR (A.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$' AND B.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$'))
    WHERE
        A.record_id <> B.record_id
        AND A.signo <> B.signo
        AND ABS(A.dmbtr - B.dmbtr) <= 0
        AND A.compensado = false
        AND B.compensado = false
) AS CompensacionesB
WHERE row_num = 1
order by dmbtr, blart;

INSERT INTO compensados
select
	saknr,
	blart,
	bldat,
	budat,
	azbet,
	dmbtr,
	sgtxt,
	belnr,
	azwae,
	hwaer,
	buzei,
	gjahr,
	compensado,
	record_id,
	signo
from
	(
	select
		saknr,
		blart,
		bldat,
		budat,
		azbet,
		dmbtr,
		sgtxt,
		belnr,
		azwae,
		hwaer,
		buzei,
		gjahr,
		compensado,
		record_id,
		signo,
		SUM(case when blart = 'EX' then dmbtr else 0 end) over (partition by budat) as suma_ex,
		SUM(case when blart = 'CP' then dmbtr else 0 end) over (partition by budat) as suma_ab,
		SUM(dmbtr) over (partition by budat) as suma_total
	from
		pa_bancarias
	where
		(blart = 'EX'
			and (sgtxt like '%DEB. COMER. PROCARD%'
				or sgtxt like '%DEB.COMER.PROCARD%'))
		or (blart = 'CP'
			and (sgtxt like '%PROCESO BANCO PAGADOR%'
				or sgtxt like '%as%'))
) as subquery
join (
	select
		budat as budat_count,
		COUNT(distinct blart) as num_tipos_documento
	from
		pa_bancarias
	group by
		budat
) as tipo_documento_counts
on
	subquery.budat = tipo_documento_counts.budat_count
where
	--ABS(suma_ex - suma_ab) <= 100
	tipo_documento_counts.num_tipos_documento = 2
order by
	subquery.budat,
	subquery.blart;

WITH ex_sumas AS (
    SELECT
        budat,
        SUM(
            CASE 
                WHEN signo = 'positivo' THEN cast(REPLACE(REPLACE(azbet, '.', ''), ',', '.') as numeric)
                WHEN signo = 'negativo' THEN -cast(REPLACE(REPLACE(azbet, '.', ''), ',', '.') as numeric)
            END
        ) AS suma_ex
    FROM pa_bancarias
    WHERE blart = '$tipoDoc_A$'
      AND (sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_A_1$%' OR sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_A_2$%')
      AND compensado = FALSE
    GROUP BY budat
),
pl_sumas AS (
    SELECT
        budat,
        SUM(
            CASE 
                WHEN signo = 'positivo' THEN cast(REPLACE(REPLACE(azbet, '.', ''), ',', '.') as numeric)
                WHEN signo = 'negativo' THEN -cast(REPLACE(REPLACE(azbet, '.', ''), ',', '.') as numeric)
            END
        ) AS suma_pl
    FROM pa_bancarias
    WHERE blart = '$tipoDoc_B$'
      AND (sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_B_1$%' OR sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_B_2$%')
      AND compensado = FALSE
    GROUP BY budat
),
sumas_iguales AS (
    SELECT
        e.budat
    FROM ex_sumas e
    JOIN pl_sumas p ON e.budat = p.budat
    --WHERE ABS(e.suma_ex + p.suma_pl) <= $limRedondeo$  -- Comparación con el límite de redondeo
)
INSERT INTO compensados (
    saknr,
    blart,
    bldat,
    budat,
    azbet,
    dmbtr,
    sgtxt,
    belnr,
    azwae,
    hwaer,
    buzei,
    gjahr,
    compensado,
    record_id,
    signo
)
SELECT
    p.saknr,
    p.blart,
    p.bldat,
    p.budat,
    p.azbet,
    p.dmbtr,
    p.sgtxt,
    p.belnr,
    p.azwae,
    p.hwaer,
    p.buzei,
    p.gjahr,
    p.compensado,
    p.record_id,
    p.signo
FROM pa_bancarias p
JOIN sumas_iguales s ON p.budat = s.budat
LEFT JOIN ex_sumas e ON p.budat = e.budat
LEFT JOIN pl_sumas l ON p.budat = l.budat
WHERE p.compensado = FALSE
  AND ((p.blart = '$tipoDoc_A$' AND (p.sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_A_1$%' OR p.sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_A_2$%')) 
       OR (p.blart = '$tipoDoc_B$' AND (p.sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_B_1$%' OR p.sgtxt ILIKE '%$textoTipoDoc_B_2$%')))
ORDER BY p.budat, p.blart;
